ZH: 我们必须勉力奋斗，才能取得成功。
EN: We must strive hard in order to succeed.

ZH: 她勉力完成了今天的工作任务。
EN: She worked hard to complete today's tasks.

ZH: 他勉力克服了困难，成功了。
EN: He overcame difficulties through hard work and succeeded.

ZH: 学生们必须勉力学习，才能取得好成绩。
EN: Students must work hard in their studies in order to achieve good grades.

ZH: 她每天都勉力地为家人做事。
EN: She works hard every day to take care of her family.

ZH: 他勉力挣了很多钱，买了一辆新车。
EN: He worked hard and earned a lot of money to buy a new car.

ZH: 我们应该勉力保持身体健康。
EN: We should strive to maintain good health.

ZH: 在新的工作中，我会勉力做到最好。
EN: In my new job, I will strive to do my best.

ZH: 勉力去帮助他人是一种美德。
EN: It is a virtue to work hard to help others.

ZH: 我会勉力完成这项任务的。
EN: I will work hard to complete this task.

ZH: 她一直勉力学习英语，现在已经很流利了。
EN: She has been working hard to learn English and now she is very fluent.

ZH: 大家都认为他能够因为他的勉力工作而取得成功。
EN: Everyone believes he can succeed because of his hard work.

ZH: 我们要不惜一切代价勉力将事情做好。
EN: We must spare no effort to do things well.

ZH: 勉力努力，永不放弃。
EN: Work hard, never give up.

ZH: 他总是勉力工作，没有拖延。
EN: He always works hard without procrastination.

ZH: 老板看到她勉力工作，给了她一份加薪。
EN: The boss saw her working hard and gave her a raise.

ZH: 他不断勉力尝试新的事情，以提高自己的技能。
EN: He keeps striving to try new things in order to improve his skills.

ZH: 我们应该勉力追求自己的梦想。
EN: We should strive to pursue our dreams.

ZH: 这个项目需要团队勉力合作才能完成。
EN: This project requires the team to work hard together to complete it.
